snippet.title: PROG: a point and click adventure.
snippet.description:
Here comes Soundwave with another game.
This time, it's a calm adventure game where you point and click through the game. Find Items and solve puzzles in a world made of cardboard and other crafting materials.



Music: Unknown, but still owns credit
